<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><?ish ishref="GUID-D3650796-0743-4A38-A09E-D30FA69E8314" version="2" lang="en-US"?><task xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" id="GUID-D3650796-0743-4A38-A09E-D30FA69E8314" xml:lang="en-US" ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3" domains="(topic task)                            (topic hi-d)                            (topic ui-d)                            (topic sw-d)                            (topic indexing-d)                            (topic ut-d)                            a(base ishcondition)                            a(base varid)                            a(base varref)                            a(base cid)                            a(base partslist)                            (topic oce-d)                            (topic sdlVariables-c)                            (topic oceCommonElements-c)                            (topic oceMetaDecl-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c task oceTask-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c hi-d oceHighlight-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c ui-d oceUi-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c sw-d oceSoftware-c)   " class="- topic/topic task/task "><title class="- topic/title "> 06 how to fill the V2 chiller with cooling liquid</title><abstract class="- topic/abstract " id="M028334-B18"><p class="- topic/p ">This documents describes the filling of the chiller with cooling liquid during the installation of the printer. 
</p></abstract><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Installation</category></metadata></prolog><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><prereq id="GUID-C71E4B56-F6A6-429E-9630-3F0443D53874" class="- topic/section task/prereq "><ol class="- topic/ol "><li id="LI_53184B16D403439F881DA2AB90C20E0F" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Power off the system</b>: 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">On the operator panel, tap on the [System] icon on the right. Tap on [Power management]. Tap on [Power off]. The system shuts down. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Switch off the power supply</b>: 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">When the system has shut down, pull to open the cover under the roll winder. Switch the power switch to the 'off' position. 
</p></li><li id="LI_4C94C73DC4F44D89B7FB313D2EFA662A" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Unplug the mains cables. 
</p></li><li id="LI_7B13AB9EBD6B4CBF9D0D9AD3BD4EB82C" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the left side cover. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">See : 
<xref keyref="24DISA038" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-47F6DCB5-4388-4055-8831-B68BB47CB03F.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 24 How to remove the left side cover (V2)?>24 How to remove the left side cover (V2)</xref> . 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the left side cover (grill). 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">See : 
<xref keyref="24DISA040" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-973B9E48-DD11-4D1A-B9E3-00530B68290A.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 24 How to remove the left side cover (grill) (V2)?>24 How to remove the left side cover (grill) (V2)</xref>. 
</p></li></ol></prereq><section id="SECTION_86EA4B5FA8464CB890FEBEE81E662603" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Required tools</title><ul id="UL_F7C509382AC7451BA612CC8861B71EA7" class="- topic/ul "><li id="LI_F1F2AA74814B4E4F9EB6648AFFB9E34A" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> 8L Cooling liquid (8 x 1L of 1070124006 (5%))
</p><p class="- topic/p "> or
</p><p class="- topic/p "> 8L Cooling liquid (1,5 x 1L of 1070073536 (25%) + 6,5L demi water)
</p></li></ul></section><section id="GUID-94C20406-75A1-4BD0-A7DB-8CD9777F04B0" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">How to fill</title><table id="NEW" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="step" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody valign="top" class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Remove the lid. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-C8A60EF4-044C-4D53-B7C3-496640F97278" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-3DFAE9B3-866E-4132-80EB-78F2BBB1DD15-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-3DFAE9B3-866E-4132-80EB-78F2BBB1DD15-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Fill the chiller with 6L cooling liquid. 
</p><note id="GUID-3C50787E-9A7A-4A53-8BF4-ED8FABA234F4" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Keep the liquid in the green range of the marker 
</p></note><note id="GUID-8E89A622-A489-432C-A90A-B0E68BAF359A" class="- topic/note "/><p class="- topic/p ">Only Cooling liquid 5% is allowed.
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Either use:
</p><p class="- topic/p ">8L Cooling liquid (8 x 1L of 1070124006 (5%))
</p><p class="- topic/p ">or
</p><p class="- topic/p ">8L Cooling liquid (1,5 x 1L of 1070073536 (25%) + 6,5L demi water)
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-688B68EB-7938-46F7-824D-8C102A74F942" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-C1FAD5F5-424D-4039-86A0-14D3DCEF3ABD-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-C1FAD5F5-424D-4039-86A0-14D3DCEF3ABD-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-2D14D4AF-69A8-49AE-97C7-E2AF5A4F4983" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-CF59A191-D626-409A-959A-732FC5059DCB-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-CF59A191-D626-409A-959A-732FC5059DCB-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Close the lid. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-5E0CA37A-F715-4ABE-9AE0-8658000951DB" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-6392E362-3083-4EEB-A7C3-AE5E918D3DE8-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-6392E362-3083-4EEB-A7C3-AE5E918D3DE8-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">4 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Roll the chiller in position. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Be sure the coolant tubes and cables are positioned properly. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">See: 
<xref href="GUID-4D0D68A4-09BC-4ECD-A279-89F6E59CE58E.xml" scope="local" format="dita" class="- topic/xref " type="task"><?ditaot gentext?>06 How to adjust the position of the chiller (V2)</xref> 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">5 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Close and lock the chiller unit. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">If previously disconnected, reconnect the earth tab. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-6C34F681-E7A2-4933-A206-A95F723CA04F" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-392F2F77-5DCF-4FA4-BF10-B6416B7C10BD-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-392F2F77-5DCF-4FA4-BF10-B6416B7C10BD-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">6 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Keep and store 3 bottles of cooling liquid for possible future service actions related to the chiller. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-0CF1F378-65AF-4B46-B46E-82F7EE70A33A.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>Installation</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
</task>